# Data sync — all tasks, all screens

Read **`AGENTS.md`** and **`src/lib/appDataTasks.ts`**.

**Any user action** must use the catalogued **`db.*` method** and show live state via **`useDB()` + `resolve*` / hooks**.

Covers: post/reel like & save, comments & replies & comment likes, follow, create/delete/report, stories, messages (send/edit/react/read), notifications, profile edit, workspace, settings, mute/fullscreen/badges, and **new tasks you add** (extend `db.ts` + `appDataTasks.ts` + AGENTS.md).

Never mirror engagement or user/post snapshots in component state. Pass **ids** into modals.
